The counter staff (both female) are very impatient and reluctant to feedback any queries. Both times I have to probe and they'll  give one word answers (just checking simple operation hours and lunch time to avoid).
This store carries a good range of products, but staff makes it a bad experience.
It's best if you just need to grab and go.
Located at the main junction at basement of Woodleigh Mall, it is a decent sized outlet have a good selection.
